Task 1b


RegrM = lm(total ~ a)
RegrM0 = lm(total ~ a - 1)

plot(a, total)
abline(RegrM, lty='dotted', col='red')
abline(RegrM0, lty='dashed', col='green')

Task 1c

phi = (sqrt(5) + 1)/2

abline(RegrM0, lty='dashed', col='green')

abline(a=0, b=phi, lty='dotdash', col='blue')
